 <p>Asmeta is a framework for the Abstract State Machines (ASMs) formal method. It is composed of different <a href="download/index.html">tools</a> for performing different validation and verification activities.</p>

<p>It is based on the definition of a <a href="metaapproach.html">metamodel</a> for ASMs. For the <strong>metamodel semantics</strong>, we adopt the ASMs semantics given in the <a href="http://www.di.unipi.it/~boerger/AsmBook/">ASM book</a>.
<!--p>A standard <strong>AsmM Library</strong> containing predefined ASM domains and functions is also provided.</p--></p>

